Scurrius' lair is located within the [[Varrock Sewers]], with the sewers being accessible via a [[manhole]] just east of [[Varrock Palace]]. The lair can be found east of the sewers entrance.

Players can enter or leave the lair by climbing through the [[broken bars]] or by crossing through [[sewage water]], respectively; there will be an approximately 15 second delay after leaving before being able to rejoin.

==Fight overview==
{{Main|Scurrius/Strategies}}
Scurrius has three attacks: his melee attack with his tail, magic attack with blue lightning being discharged, and a ranged attack of stinky fur balls being thrown at players. The fight is split into three phases; Scurrius may heal from the [[Food Pile]]s between each phase. While he is eating, he has a slight damage reduction applied to him. Scurrius may also summon six [[Giant rat (Scurrius)|giant rat]]s to aid him during the fight.

